If you want a specific unit constructed, you may direct me to locate an idle facility and build that unit to a destination of your choosing.  To instruct me to build a unit, close this message window, right-click on my image in the Command Center, select 'Build Ships', 'Build Troops' or 'Build Facilities' from the menu, and use the target cursor to select a destination to which the unit should be built.  The Build Window will then come up; select the unit and quantity of that unit you wish constructed, then click the check-mark at the bottom of the build window so that I may carry out your orders.